Tasks for NOCC. If you think something is missing here,
please send a note to <nocc-discuss at lists.sourceforge.net>
or file a RFE at:
http://sf.net/tracker/?atid=362177&group_id=12177&func=browse

 - Switch all charsets to UTF-8, as per:
    http://www.joelonsoftware.com/articles/Unicode.html
 - Change language files to use an array ($lang_text->...).
 - Create specific icons for attachments.
 - Colored quotes.
 - RFC 1894 support (Delivery Status Notification).
 - Dynamic Gzip support: allows live display compression, might speed up when
   connected through slow lines.
 - Switch to pure CSS for color backgrounds, get rid of tables, switch to divs.
    o use theme templates.
 - Printer-friendly e-mail formatting.
 - Webmail user documentation.
